Text:
Thanks, except for the number.


As of today, 2011-06-17, dofantasy, the originaters of this comics series does not list any title under number 246. Nor does a search for "Vampire Realm" yield anything.
Actually, this IS a Fansadox comic called Vampire Realm.  Since their website doesn't list a #246, I can only assume that they removed it from their catalog for some reason.
